      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DETECTABLE (4) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 25.41 beating KRIS BAR IMOGEN. Has a tricky draw to overcome but has a good record over this journey. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. The one to beat again. SCOTT EPHRAIM (3) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 25.47. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Leading player again. KRIS BAR IMOGEN (5) improved her time on first attempt here at the trip with a 2.25 lengths second in 25.56 latest. Will be in this for a long way. FLYING ROGUE (2) must be included in main hopes on latest effort.",
